You can purchase up to 10 packages of each type. Once you unlock the final package, you will be able to purchase an unlimited number of packages.</p><p>To purchase a license package:</p> <ol> <li> <p>From your Company profile or the homepage menu, click on &quot;Invites and packages&quot;.</p> </li> <li> <p>Enter the &quot;Packages&quot; section.</p> </li> <li> <p>Select the number of unlocked packages that meet your needs and proceed with the purchase by choosing between bank transfer or credit card.</p> </li> </ol> <ul> <li> <p>If paying by bank transfer, you will receive instructions to complete the payment, and the package will need to be manually renewed each year.</p> </li> <li> <p>If paying by credit card, you will be redirected to Stripe to complete the payment.<br>Additionally, each package lasts for one year and renews automatically.&nbsp;</p> </li> </ul> <p>You can change the payment method or cancel the package up to the day before the package&rsquo;s expiration.</p> <p>To cancel a license package:</p> <ol> <li> <p>Click on &quot;Account and plan&quot; in your Company profile or the homepage menu.</p> </li> <li> <p>Go to the &quot;Subscription&quot; section.</p> </li> <li> <p>Click &quot;Manage subscription&quot;, where you will see a summary of your active plans. You can manage the payment details of each plan or choose to cancel your subscription at any time.</p> </li> </ol>'),
	 (N'it',N'Come posso invitare altri utenti?',N'<p>L&rsquo;utente Admin pu&ograve; invitare Team Member (inclusi nell&rsquo;abbonamento) e/o Viewer (dietro acquisto di una licenza) cliccando su&nbsp;&ldquo;Inviti e pacchetti&rdquo;&nbsp;all&rsquo;interno del Profilo azienda o del menu principale in home page.<br>All&rsquo;interno della maschera inviti:</p> <ol> <li> <p>Clicca su &ldquo;Invita utenti&rdquo;.</p> </li> <li> <p>Seleziona la tipologia di utenti da invitare.</p> </li> </ol> <p>Qui si aprir&agrave; un modale per importare gli indirizzi e-mail degli utenti che si desiderano invitare e infine inviare l&rsquo;invito.</p>'),
	 (N'en',N'How can I invite other users?',N'<p><strong>How can I invite other users?</strong><strong><br></strong>The Admin user can invite Team Members (included in the subscription) and/or Viewers (with the purchase of a license) by clicking on &quot;Invites and packages&quot; in the Company profile or in the main menu on the homepage.<br>Within the invite section:</p> <ol> <li> <p>Click on &quot;Invite users&quot;.</p> </li> <li> <p>Select the type of users you want to invite.<br>A pop-up window will appear where you can import the email addresses of the users you wish to invite and send the invitation.</p> </li> </ol>');

